@startuml MyAIStorybook_SSD_Voice_Input
title MyAIStorybook - System Sequence Diagram: Voice Input Story Generation Scenario

actor "User" as User
participant ":System" as System

note over User, System
    Voice Input Story Generation Scenario (Main Success)
    System is treated as BLACK BOX
end note

User -> System : makeNewStory()

User -> System : recordVoiceInput()
System --> User : recording_started

User -> System : stopRecording(audio_data)
System --> User : transcription(text)

User -> System : confirmPrompt(confirmed_text)
System --> User : prompt_confirmed

User -> System : selectOptions(generate_images, mode)

User -> System : generateStory()
System --> User : story_with_images(title, scenes[], images[])

note right of System
    System converts voice to text internally
    using Speech-to-Text
    Then proceeds with normal generation
end note

@enduml
